    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  children 2-16 years of age

          -  scheduled for polysomnogram

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  cardiovascular, neuromuscular, immunologic or craniofacial disorders

          -  pharmacologic treatment including corticosteroids and leukotriene receptor
             antagonists in the last month

          -  subjects who have already received treatment for OSA with an oral appliance,
             continuous positive airway pressure (CPAP) device

          -  previously undergone tonsillectomy and/or adenoidectomy
      </textblock>
